  "browser_support": "All browsers.",
  "performance_notes": "One spinner rotation while loading; trivial.",
  "accessibility_notes": "Set disabled + aria-busy='true' during loading so it can't be double-submitted and assistive tech knows it's working. Keep the button width stable to avoid layout shift. Restore state on completion/error.",
